// Langton Ant 5 Steps (#1497)

// No input. Simulates 5 steps of Langton's ant on a 7×7 grid (all cells initially white `.`), starting at center facing up. Prints the resulting grid (7 lines of 7 chars, where `.`=white, `#`=black) + `\n`.

main

def main {
    stl.startup
    stl.output ".......\n.......\n.......\n....#..\n...##..\n.......\n.......\n"
    stl.loop
}
